name: Teymoor
description:
Hey,
My name is Teymoor and I am a stray cat living in the street, A beautiful soul having an eye on me and each time I visit her she feeds me in the balcony or she leave food behind the door, By purchesing my NFT you will help to support me and my pals who also lives in the street.

I love and support stray animals. The sales profit of this collection will be used to support a few individual shelter who does rescue animals. To see the cats story visit @6lovely.cats on Instagram.

Illustrations by @manisaemi
